(8, 'Giant snake found in tree canopy in Belgrade.', '\r\nIn a surprising incident this morning, a majestic snake was sighted coiled up on a tree branch in the vibrant neighborhood of Vračar, located in the heart of Belgrade. ', 'Belgrade, Serbia - A scene straight out of a wildlife documentary unfolded this morning in the picturesque Vračar neighborhood of Belgrade, as a majestic snake perched high on a tree, capturing the attention and awe of onlookers. The unusual sighting serves as a vivid reminder of the harmonious coexistence between nature and urban life within this bustling city.\r\n\r\nEyewitnesses were treated to a mesmerizing spectacle as the snake, its sinuous body gracefully coiled, found its temporary refuge in the leafy canopy. The creature\'s striking appearance, with its vibrant scales glimmering in the sunlight, held spectators spellbound. Cell phones were quickly pulled out, capturing photos and videos of this unexpected encounter with nature\'s splendor.\r\n\r\nAuthorities were promptly alerted to ensure the safety of both the public and the snake. Wildlife experts and trained professionals arrived on the scene to assess the situation and formulate a plan for the creature\'s safe removal. Respecting the delicate balance between urban development and wildlife preservation, measures were taken to minimize disruption to the snake\'s natural habitat.\r\n\r\nBelgrade, known for its captivating architecture and bustling city life, rarely witnesses such encounters with wildlife within its borders. The sighting in Vračar serves as a gentle reminder that even in the heart of a metropolis, nature finds a way to thrive and surprise us.\r\n\r\nThe presence of this awe-inspiring snake underscores the importance of preserving green spaces within urban areas. Parks, gardens, and trees not only provide essential habitats for diverse species but also offer residents a connection to the natural world, fostering a sense of tranquility and appreciation for the environment.\r\n\r\nAs news of the snake\'s sighting spread, residents and nature enthusiasts flocked to the area, hoping to catch a glimpse of this enigmatic visitor. Local authorities, recognizing the public\'s fascination, organized educational sessions and discussions on wildlife conservation and the importance of coexistence.\r\n\r\nThis remarkable encounter will undoubtedly be remembered as a testament to the delicate balance between urbanization and preserving the natural world. Belgrade\'s Vračar neighborhood will forever hold the memory of this majestic snake, serving as a reminder of the unexpected beauty that can be found in the unlikeliest of places.\r\n\r\nAs the snake is safely relocated to an appropriate habitat, the incident serves as a call to action for both residents and authorities to continue valuing and protecting the biodiversity that thrives alongside the city\'s bustling streets. It is a reminder that even amidst the concrete and steel, nature finds a way to inspire and awe, inviting us to embrace the profound wonders of the natural world.\r\n\r\nIn a world often dominated by human progress, the sighting of this snake on a tree branch in Belgrade\'s Vračar neighborhood is a gentle reminder that we are all interconnected, sharing th', 'news', 'zmija.jpg', 'Yes'),
(9, 'ZET bus engulfed in flames', 'Earlier today, around 2 PM, a ZET bus caught fire while in motion in the western part of Zagreb.', '\r\nToday, shortly before 2 PM, a ZET bus caught fire while in motion in the western part of Zagreb. The bus driver immediately attempted to extinguish the fire but was unsuccessful, prompting firefighters to rush to the scene to provide assistance.\r\n\r\nDespite the efforts to contain the blaze, it quickly spread to two other vehicles before it was completely extinguished. The incident took place on Hercegovačka Street, which has been closed off to traffic, diverting vehicles to surrounding streets.\r\n\r\nThe swift response of the bus driver in attempting to tackle the fire highlights the importance of prompt action during such emergencies. The assistance of firefighters was crucial in bringing the situation under control and preventing further damage or injuries.\r\n\r\nAs investigations into the cause of the fire are underway, authorities are working to ensure the safety of the area and minimize any disruption to local residents and commuters. Traffic management measures have been put in place to redirect vehicles and ensure smooth flow in the vicinity.\r\n\r\nEvents like this serve as a reminder of the potential risks associated with public transportation and the importance of maintaining safety protocols. The incident also highlights the commendable efforts of emergency responders who put their lives on the line to protect the community.\r\n\r\nWhile the incident may cause temporary inconvenience to commuters and residents, it is crucial to prioritize safety and thorough investigation to prevent similar incidents in the future. Authorities will be working diligently to determine the cause of the fire and implement any necessary measures to enhance safety protocols.\r\n\r\nAs the affected vehicles are being removed from the scene and the area is being cleared, it is expected that normal traffic flow will resume soon. Local authorities will continue to provide updates and ensure the necessary support for those affected by the incident.\r\n\r\nEfforts will be made to assess any potential damages to the infrastructure and facilitate the repair process swiftly. The incident serves as a reminder for both the public and transportation authorities to remain vigilant and proactive in maintaining safety standards to safeguard passengers and the community.\r\n\r\nWhile incidents like this are unfortunate, they provide valuable lessons and opportunities for improvement in emergency response and safety procedures. By learning from such events, transportation systems can become more resilient and better equipped to handle unforeseen circumstances in the future.', 'news', 'bus.jpg', 'Yes'),
(10, 'Missing submarine used for Titanic tours', 'Submarine used for transporting people to see the Titanic wreckage reported missing in the Atlantic Ocean, prompting a search and rescue mission, according to BBC.', 'In a startling development, a submarine used for transporting individuals to explore the fabled remains of the Titanic has gone missing in the vast expanse of the Atlantic Ocean. The news, reported by the BBC today, has ignited a massive search and rescue operation to locate the vanished vessel and ensure the safety of all those on board.\r\n\r\nThe submarine, specifically designed for underwater tourism and exploration, embarked on its ill-fated journey with a team of renowned researchers and experts on board. These experts, well-versed in maritime history and underwater archaeology, had dedicated their careers to unraveling the secrets and stories hidden beneath the depths.\r\n\r\nAs news of the disappearance spread, concern and speculation gripped both the maritime and tourism communities. The submarine, a vital link for enthusiasts wishing to witness the Titanic\'s haunting remains firsthand, was cherished for providing a unique and awe-inspiring experience.\r\n\r\nThe search and rescue mission, led by international maritime authorities and supported by advanced technologies, has been tirelessly scouring the depths of the ocean in an effort to locate any trace of the missing submarine. Time is of the essence as every passing moment decreases the chances of a successful rescue operation.\r\n\r\nThe loss of the submarine not only raises questions about the safety protocols and risks associated with underwater exploration but also highlights the immense challenges faced by researchers and adventurers venturing into the deep unknown. The unforgiving nature of the ocean reminds us of its untamed power and the need for caution when delving into its mysteries.\r\n\r\nEfforts to locate the missing submarine have been met with numerous obstacles, including treacherous underwater conditions and the vastness of the search area. As days turn into weeks, the urgency to locate the vessel and its occupants intensifies, as hopes persist for a successful outcome.\r\n\r\nThe disappearance of this esteemed submarine, along with its team of acclaimed researchers, serves as a stark reminder of the perils faced by those who seek to uncover the secrets of the deep. The commitment and passion demonstrated by these individuals in their pursuit of knowledge and understanding are a testament to the resilience and curiosity of the human spirit.\r\n\r\nAs the search and rescue mission presses forward, the maritime and scientific communities, as well as the wider public, anxiously await updates and pray for a positive resolution. The lost submarine, once a vessel of discovery and wonder, now finds itself at the center of a desperate search, a poignant reminder of the inherent risks and uncertainties of exploration.\r\n\r\nWhile the circumstances surrounding the submarine\'s disappearance remain shrouded in mystery, this incident serves as a call for increased safety measures and stringent protocols in underwater tourism and exploration. The determination to learn from this tragedy will drive future advanc', 'news', 'podmornica.jpg', 'No'),
(12, 'Fire at Sarajevo prison spreads around', '\r\nToday afternoon, a fire broke out on the fifth floor of the Sarajevo Penitentiary. The fire spread to the building of the Municipal and Cantonal Court.', 'In a shocking turn of events, a fierce fire erupted on the fifth floor of the Sarajevo Penitentiary this afternoon, quickly engulfing the entire floor. The flames then spread rapidly, engulfing the nearby building housing the Municipal and Cantonal Court. The incident has led to significant disruption and prompted an urgent response from the emergency services.\r\n\r\nThe cause of the fire is yet to be determined, with investigations currently underway. Firefighters, alongside prison and court staff, worked tirelessly to evacuate inmates and court personnel to safety. The swift response and coordinated efforts of the emergency teams undoubtedly helped minimize the potential for casualties.\r\n\r\nAs the fire raged on, thick plumes of smoke billowed into the sky, attracting the attention of onlookers and causing concern among residents and passersby. The incident has sent shockwaves through the community, underscoring the importance of robust fire safety measures in institutional settings.\r\n\r\nThe Municipal and Cantonal Court, an essential pillar of the local judicial system, suffered extensive damage due to the spreading flames. The exact extent of the damage is yet to be assessed, but initial reports indicate significant structural and property loss.\r\n\r\nThe aftermath of the incident saw the mobilization of additional fire brigades and emergency response teams to contain the blaze and prevent its further spread. The resilience and dedication of these professionals in the face of adversity are commendable.\r\n\r\nAuthorities swiftly cordoned off the affected areas, diverting traffic and urging nearby residents to stay clear of the scene. The safety of all individuals involved, including inmates, court personnel, and emergency responders, remained the top priority throughout the operation.\r\n\r\nWhile the incident caused disruption to ongoing court proceedings and administrative activities, efforts are being made to ensure the resumption of essential judicial functions as swiftly as possible. The cooperation and understanding of all parties involved will be crucial in overcoming the challenges presented by this unexpected event.\r\n\r\nAs investigations progress, it is hoped that the root cause of the fire will be determined, allowing authorities to implement necessary measures to prevent similar incidents in the future. Additionally, steps will be taken to assess the structural integrity of the affected buildings and expedite the repair and restoration process.\r\n\r\nThe incident serves as a stark reminder of the vulnerability of critical institutions and the importance of robust fire safety protocols. It highlights the need for continuous training, regular safety drills, and vigilant monitoring to prevent such incidents from occurring.\r\n\r\nThe local community and judicial authorities are united in their resolve to overcome the aftermath of this devastating fire. As the recovery and reconstruction efforts begin, support and solidarity from neighboring communities and rel', 'news', 'pozar.jpg', 'No'),
(14, 'What can prevent Kovačić from joining Manchester?', 'Mateo Kovačić is very close to joining Manchester City, according to Fabrizio Romano. The deal is in its final stages.', 'In a development that has captured the attention of football fans and pundits alike, Croatian midfielder Mateo Kovačić is reportedly on the verge of completing a move to Premier League champions Manchester City. Renowned transfer expert Fabrizio Romano has revealed that negotiations between the player and the club are in their final stages, raising the prospect of an imminent transfer.\r\n\r\nKovačić, known for his technical prowess, vision, and ability to control the midfield, has been a key player for Chelsea in recent seasons. However, the opportunity to join Manchester City has emerged as an enticing prospect for the Croatian international, who is eager to test his skills in one of Europe\'s top leagues.\r\n\r\nThe potential move to Manchester City comes as no surprise given the club\'s track record of success and their ambition to strengthen their squad further. Under the guidance of manager Pep Guardiola, the team has achieved remarkable success domestically and consistently competed at the highest level in European competitions.\r\n\r\nShould the deal be finalized, Kovačić would bring a wealth of experience and quality to an already talented Manchester City midfield. Known for his impeccable ball control, intelligent passing, and ability to break opposition lines, the Croatian midfielder would undoubtedly bolster the team\'s creativity and enhance their attacking capabilities.\r\n\r\nWhile details of the transfer fee and contract terms remain undisclosed, it is clear that Manchester City views Kovačić as a valuable addition to their squad. His versatility and adaptability would provide Guardiola with additional options and tactical flexibility, allowing the manager to deploy him in various midfield roles depending on the team\'s needs.\r\n\r\nThe potential move to Manchester City holds significant implications for both Kovačić\'s career and the landscape of English football. Playing alongside some of the world\'s best players and under the tutelage of Guardiola could provide the Croatian midfielder with a platform to further develop and showcase his skills on the big stage.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, Kovačić\'s potential arrival would strengthen Manchester City\'s already formidable squad, adding depth and competition for places in midfield. The increased competition within the team could further spur the players to perform at their best and contribute to Manchester City\'s pursuit of domestic and European success in the upcoming season.\r\n\r\nAs with any transfer, there are always variables and potential hurdles that could arise in the final stages of negotiations. However, the reported progress in talks between Kovačić and Manchester City has fueled anticipation among fans, who eagerly await an official announcement regarding the player\'s transfer.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Mateo Kovačić\'s imminent move to Manchester City marks an exciting development in the football world. If the deal is finalized, the Croatian midfielder would join a star-studded squad and have the opportunity to make ', 'sport', 'kovacic.jpg', 'No'),
(15, 'Elvis in disbelief over Brozović\'s move in extra time', 'Former Croatian footballer Elvis Brajković (54), who played for the national team in the 1990s, commented on the UEFA Nations League final, in which coach Zlatko Dalić\'s team lost to Spain in a penalty shootout.', 'Former Croatian footballer Elvis Brajković (54), who played for the national team in the 1990s, commented on the UEFA Nations League final, in which coach Zlatko Dalić\'s team lost to Spain in a penalty shootout. The regular time and extra time ended in a 0-0 draw. Goalkeeper Unai Simon made saves against Lovro Majer and Bruno Petković, while Aymeric Laporte hit the crossbar for Spain.\r\n\r\n\"There is regret. The luck of the penalty shootout was not on our side, unlike the last two World Cups. Spain is a well-organized team, rejuvenated in the meantime, with less glamorous names but showing quality. We played at a high level, matching them in possession.\r\n\r\nThe match was relatively even, and the penalty shootout ultimately decided the winner. I haven\'t seen such excellent penalty execution in a long time. Until Majer\'s shot, the penalties were top-notch. Livaković, who is excellent at saving penalties, couldn\'t make any saves,\" said Brajković in an interview with Radio Rijeka.', 'sport', 'brozovic.jpg', 'Yes'),
(16, 'Armenia overtakes Croatia and claims the top spot in the qualifi', 'Armenia defeated Latvia 2-1 in the fourth round of Group D qualifiers for the European Championship.', 'Armenia secured a 2-1 victory over Latvia in the fourth round of Group D qualifiers for the European Championship. The Armenians took the lead in the 35th minute through a goal by Nair Tiknizyan, who struck from close range after a sharp cross from Artak Dashjan on the right side. The visitors equalized in the 67th minute when Roberts Savalnieks unleashed a powerful shot from nearly 30 meters, finding the bottom corner of the Armenian net.\r\n\r\nHowever, Armenia managed to clinch the victory in the closing stages of the match when Tigran Barseghyan scored from a penalty awarded for a handball in the first minute of stoppage time. This marks Armenia\'s second win in the group, following their triumph over Wales (4-2), putting them on six points and temporarily taking the top spot. Turkey also has six points but a lower goal difference. Latvia remains at the bottom of the group without any points.', 'sport', 'armenija.jpg', 'Yes'),
(17, ' We all know where Mbappe wants to play.', 'Reporters asked Manchester City manager Pep Guardiola if he will sign Kylian Mbappe (24).', 'In the world of football transfer rumors, few names generate as much excitement as Kylian Mbappe. The young French superstar has been a subject of much speculation regarding his future, and Manchester City has emerged as one of the clubs linked with his potential signing. The media wasted no time in probing City manager Pep Guardiola about this matter during a recent press conference.\r\n\r\nWhen questioned about the possibility of acquiring Mbappe\'s services, Guardiola maintained a composed demeanor while acknowledging the talent and appeal of the 24-year-old forward. He emphasized that Mbappe is a fantastic player who can make a difference in any team. However, Guardiola tactfully dodged providing any direct confirmation or denial regarding the transfer speculations.\r\n\r\nGuardiola highlighted the fact that Mbappe currently belongs to another club, and it would be inappropriate to discuss potential transfers out of respect for both the player and his current team. He expressed his admiration for the French international and his desire to see the talented forward excel in his career.\r\n\r\nThe manager\'s response left the door open to interpretation, fueling further discussions among football enthusiasts and analysts. While Guardiola did not explicitly confirm Manchester City\'s interest in Mbappe, his praise for the player\'s abilities only added to the excitement surrounding the potential move.\r\n\r\nMbappe, who has made a name for himself at Paris Saint-Germain, has consistently been regarded as one of the brightest young talents in the world of football. His blistering pace, exceptional skills, and goal-scoring prowess have captured the attention of top clubs across Europe. With his contract set to expire in the near future, speculations about his next destination have intensified.\r\n\r\nManchester City, known for its ambition and financial prowess, has often been associated with high-profile transfers in recent years. The club\'s potential pursuit of Mbappe raises intriguing possibilities for the team\'s already formidable attack, which includes the likes of Kevin De Bruyne and Raheem Sterling.\r\n\r\nAs the transfer window progresses, football fans eagerly await any official announcements regarding Mbappe\'s future. While Guardiola\'s response may have left some room for speculation, only time will tell whether Manchester City will make a bold move for the talented French forward.\r\n\r\nIn the world of football, surprises are not uncommon, and Mbappe\'s potential move to Manchester City would undoubtedly be a seismic event that could reshape the dynamics of the sport. For now, fans and pundits can only speculate and eagerly anticipate what the future holds for one of football\'s brightest stars.', 'sport', 'mbappe.jpg', 'Yes'),
(20, 'A Turkish journalist: I spoke with Dinamo about Livaković', 'Dinamo and Croatian national team goalkeeper Dominik Livaković has concluded his appearances in the Nations League, and it appears that he will have an uncertain summer transfer window.', 'Goalkeeper Dominik Livaković, who represents both Dinamo Zagreb and the Croatian national team, has completed his performances in the Nations League. As the summer transfer window approaches, Livaković\'s future remains uncertain, with potential moves on the horizon.\r\n\r\nThe End of Nations League Campaign:\r\n\r\nLivaković recently wrapped up his appearances in the Nations League, where he showcased his exceptional goalkeeping skills. His performances for Croatia were notable, with impressive saves and commanding presence in the penalty area.\r\n\r\nTransfer Speculations:\r\n\r\nWith his remarkable displays attracting attention from clubs across Europe, Livaković\'s future has become a subject of intense speculation. Several reports suggest that his impressive performances have caught the eye of several top-tier clubs seeking to strengthen their goalkeeping options.\r\n\r\nUncertainty Surrounding the Summer Transfer Window:\r\n\r\nAs the summer transfer window looms, uncertainty hangs over Livaković\'s next career move. The Croatian goalkeeper finds himself at a crucial juncture, evaluating potential offers and weighing his options for the upcoming season.\r\n\r\nClub Loyalty and Market Interest:\r\n\r\nDespite the growing interest from other clubs, Livaković has maintained his loyalty to Dinamo Zagreb, the club where he has honed his skills and made a name for himself. However, with increased market interest, it remains to be seen whether he will continue his journey with Dinamo or seek a new challenge at a different club.\r\n\r\nThe Decision-Making Process:\r\n\r\nLivaković and his team are expected to carefully assess the opportunities and evaluate the best career move for the talented goalkeeper. Factors such as the sporting project, the level of competition, and potential playing time will play a pivotal role in shaping his decision.\r\n\r\nNational Team Commitments:\r\n\r\nAmidst the transfer speculations, Livaković will continue to focus on his responsibilities with the Croatian national team. As one of their key players, he will aim to contribute to their success in upcoming international competitions.\r\n\r\nConclusion:\r\n\r\nDominik Livaković\'s performances in the Nations League have put him in the spotlight, attracting attention from clubs across Europe. As the summer transfer window approaches, his future remains uncertain, with potential moves on the horizon. Whether he stays loyal to Dinamo Zagreb or embarks on a new chapter in his career, one thing is certain – Livaković\'s talent and potential make him an exciting prospect for any club in need of a top-quality goalkeeper.', 'sport', 'livakovic.jpg', 'Yes'),
(21, 'Tuttomercato: Dinamo has signed a striker', '\r\nMONSEF BAKRAR, a 22-year-old Algerian striker, is set to join Dinamo this summer, according to Italian Tuttomercato.', '\r\n\r\nIn an exciting transfer development, Dinamo Zagreb, the Croatian football club, is on the verge of signing 22-year-old Algerian striker Monsef Bakrar. The news broke through Italian sports outlet Tuttomercato, indicating that Bakrar\'s arrival at Dinamo is expected to take place during the upcoming summer transfer window. The potential acquisition of the talented young forward has sparked anticipation among football enthusiasts, eager to witness his skills on the pitch.\r\n\r\nMonsef Bakrar, known for his impressive performances and burgeoning potential, has caught the attention of football scouts around Europe. At the tender age of 22, the Algerian striker has already showcased his abilities in various leagues and competitions, leaving a lasting impression with his goal-scoring prowess and technical finesse. Bakrar\'s remarkable development has earned him recognition as one of the most promising young talents in Algerian football.\r\n\r\nDinamo Zagreb\'s Ambition:\r\nDinamo Zagreb, a prominent club in Croatian football, has a reputation for nurturing and developing young talents into top-class players. With an impressive track record of producing and exporting skilled footballers, Dinamo\'s interest in Bakrar reflects their commitment to maintaining a competitive squad and securing long-term success. The club\'s decision to pursue the Algerian striker highlights their belief in his abilities and the potential impact he can make in their upcoming campaigns.\r\n\r\nPotential Partnership:\r\nBakrar\'s arrival at Dinamo Zagreb could pave the way for an exciting partnership with the club\'s existing attacking players. His natural goal-scoring instincts, combined with his technical ability, would add a new dimension to Dinamo\'s offensive options. The anticipated collaboration with seasoned players and the club\'s renowned coaching staff could prove instrumental in Bakrar\'s further development, allowing him to flourish on the professional stage.\r\n\r\nThe Algerian Influence:\r\nBakrar\'s addition to Dinamo Zagreb would also enhance the club\'s multicultural fabric, adding to the diversity and global appeal of the team. Algerian footballers have consistently showcased their talent and adaptability in various leagues worldwide, and Bakrar\'s arrival would strengthen the presence of Algerian players in Croatian football. This exchange of footballing cultures and experiences can foster an environment of growth and unity within the club.\r\n\r\nConclusion:\r\nThe news of Monsef Bakrar\'s potential transfer to Dinamo Zagreb has stirred excitement among fans and pundits alike. As the 22-year-old Algerian striker prepares to embark on a new chapter in his career, the stage is set for him to make a lasting impact in Croatian football. With Dinamo Zagreb\'s proven track record of developing young talents, Bakrar\'s arrival promises to be an exciting prospect for both the club and the player. Football enthusiasts eagerly await the official announcement, eager to witness Bakrar\'s talent unfold in the', 'Sport', 'dinamo.jpg', 'No'),
(22, 'Saudi Arabia has withdrawn from the 2030 World Cup', 'SAUDI ARABIA has dropped out of the race to host the 2030 FIFA World Cup, as reported by Marca.', 'Saudi Arabia believes it is impossible to compete with the joint hosting project led by Spain and Portugal, with the potential addition of Morocco. \"It is Europe\'s turn to host the major international football tournament,\" reports Marca, quoting Saudi officials.\r\n\r\nSaudi Arabia will now focus on bidding for the 2034 FIFA World Cup. The only other candidacy that will rival Spain, Portugal, and Morocco is the South American quartet composed of Argentina, Uruguay, Chile, and Paraguay. The hosts of the 2030 World Cup will be announced in September of next year.', 'Sport', 'saudarab.jpg', 'No'),
(29, 'Five dead in \"catastrophic implosion\"', 'Five people aboard the missing submarine Titan were killed', 'Five people aboard the missing submarine Titan were killed in a \"catastrophic implosion,\" stated a Coast Guard official yesterday, bringing an end to the extensive search for the vessel lost during its journey to the Titanic.\r\nAn unmanned underwater robot deployed from a Canadian vessel discovered the submarine wreckage yesterday morning approximately 488 meters from the bow of the century-old wreckage, 2-1/2 miles (4 km) below the surface, said Rear Admiral John Mauger of the United States Coast Guard during a press conference.\r\n', 'News', 'podmornica.jpg', 'Yes'),
(30, 'Zagreb is acquiring 11 used trams', '\r\nThe City of Zagreb has announced an international public tender for the procurement of 11 used trams, with an estimated value of 2,700,000 euros.\r\n', 'The City of Zagreb has announced an international public tender for the procurement of 11 used trams, with an estimated value of 2,700,000 euros (excluding VAT), and the expected delivery period is from October 2023 to December 2024, according to information obtained by Hina from the city administration on Friday.\r\n\"Taking care of the essential public transportation service for the 800,000 citizens who rely on the daily services provided by ZET (Zagreb Electric Tram), the City of Zagreb has announced an international public tender for the procurement of 11 used trams. This is an open procedure for public procurement, and the deadline for submitting bids is July 21st,\" stated the Zagreb city administration. They emphasize that investments in public transportation in Zagreb have been neglected for decades. Along with the purchase of 20 new trams, expected to be delivered in 2025, acquiring used trams is necessary for ZET to maintain a reliable schedule until the arrival of these 20 new trams.\r\n\"Due to the fact that trams almost 50 years old operate on Zagreb\'s streets, which require demanding maintenance and the procurement of spare parts, the City of Zagreb, which is now making significant investments in purchasing new trams, is simultaneously investing in the procurement of used trams,\" highlighted the city administration.\r\n', 'News', 'tramvaj.jpg', 'No'),
(39, 'Zg: 50,000 sterile mosquitoes have been released', 'To combat mosquitoes, 50,000 sterile male tiger mosquitoes were released in the in Zagreb.', 'To combat mosquitoes, today 50,000 sterile male tiger mosquitoes were released in the Cvjetno naselje neighborhood in Zagreb as part of a pilot project for mosquito control using a method implemented in several EU countries.\r\nThis involves the Sterile Insect Technique (SIT), a biological method for mosquito control, which involves releasing sterile male mosquitoes into the environment. They mate with wild females of the same species in the area where they are released, resulting in females laying eggs that will not develop into new mosquito individuals,\" explained Ana Klobučar, the Head of the Disinfection, Disinfestation, and Pest Control Department at the Institute of Public Health Dr. Andrija Štampar. Releasing a sufficient number of sterile males over an extended period allows for mating with a large number of females, ultimately leading to a significant reduction in the population of tiger mosquitoes in that area.\r\nNext week, an additional 50,000 mosquito individuals will be released in the Cvjetno naselje area, bringing the total number to 100,000. The invasive species Aedes albopictus, commonly known as the tiger mosquito, has become established in Zagreb.\r\n', 'News', 'komarci.jpg', 'No');

